  <user-story>
    <as-a>maker</as-a>
    <i-want>to receive time-sensitive alerts for my listings</i-want>
    <so-that>I can respond promptly and avoid SLA violations or missed opportunities</so-that>
  </user-story>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion id="ac1">Maker receives immediate push notification when first qualifying offer received on listing (≥ minimum price), triggering 72-hour auction countdown.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac2">Maker receives push notification when new bid placed on active auction, including bid amount and current high bidder status.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac3">**SLA CRITICAL**: Maker receives escalating alerts for shipping tracking requirement (24h, 48h, 72h warnings) before SLA violation.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac4">Maker receives push notification when auction enters final 15 minutes (soft-close period) with option to accept current high bid immediately.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac5">Maker receives push notification when payment received, triggering fulfillment workflow with 72-hour tracking requirement countdown.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac6">**BUSINESS CRITICAL**: Maker can accept current high bid from notification action button, immediately ending auction and entering payment window.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac7">Maker dashboard shows SLA status indicators for all active orders with color-coded urgency (green/yellow/red) and time remaining.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
